Lines.Comment: 'killing spree' Said as if she's lowering herself to use the layman's phrasing.
We're allies for now. Let us focus on our true foes.
Do you truly think you are worthy to fight by my side?
I thought I was done suffering fools.
Oh, how your soul shall suffer for that.
Hmm, you... this presents an unfortunate complication.
I look forward to snapping your bones one by one.
I have no time to waste on you.
It is unwise to provoke a Sentinel.
We remain allied through convenience. Do not make it, inconvenient.
I do not know why the Light answers you. But I hope it can redeem you.
You. How dare you call upon the Light for such twisted atrocities.
They call you a hero? Hah. I've scraped more muck off my boot that was more heroic.
The Light shines on us all.
Will pull from one of her laugh lines.
Moment of weakness. Calling out to her lost love.
